@startuml BasicUserUseCase

' Using default plantuml due to C4 model library not supporting use cases.
' src: https://plantuml.com/use-case-diagram

title Use Case – Basic User Browsing Restaurant Menus

actor "Basic User" as BasicUser

rectangle "Lounastutka Web Application" {
  usecase "Open Website" as UC1
  usecase "View Map with Restaurants" as UC2
  usecase "Select Restaurant Pin" as UC3
  usecase "View Restaurant Details\n(Menu, Address, Name, etc.)" as UC4
  usecase "Leave Website" as UC5
}

' Relations
BasicUser --> UC1 : navigates to
BasicUser --> UC2 : browses
BasicUser --> UC3 : selects
BasicUser --> UC4 : reads
BasicUser --> UC5 : closes session

UC1 --> UC2 : loads map
UC2 --> UC3 : shows pins
UC3 --> UC4 : loads details

legend right
    | Symbol| Meaning |
    | Rectangle | Boundary |
    | Stickman | User |
    | Ellipse | Use-case |
    | Arrow | Action |
endlegend

@enduml
